      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃なら大丈夫だよ。なんせ遙子さんのお墨付きだしな\n琴乃ならきっと……ウエディングドレスを着こなせるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'll be fine‚ Kotono. After all‚ you have Haruko-san's approval.\nI'm sure Kotono will be able to pull off a wedding dress beautifully.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0666666667,
